## APPENDIX 2 ‚Äì HIGH-RISK AI SYSTEM CATEGORIES

1. Biometric identification and categorization
1. Critical infrastructure management
1. Educational and vocational training scoring
1. Employment, worker management, and access to self-employment
1. Access to essential private and public services
1. Law enforcement (predictive policing, evidence assessment, offender risk assessment)
1. Migration, asylum, and border control management
1. Administration of justice and democratic processes
1. Autonomous weapons systems
1. Financial services creditworthiness and risk assessment

